{"id":27,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":27,"title":"Guide to the Friend","subtitle":"","short_title":"Guide to the Friend","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.head1"},[".seriesTitle","Guide to the",["span.emphasis","Friend"]],[".title","Possible Ideas for Family Home Evening"]],[".bodyBlock",[".figure",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.f1"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],["p.para","Read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/07/save-her.p1"},"“Save Her!”"],"(pages 2–3). Play the Safety Circle game together and talk about things your family can do to help others."]],["li",["span.label","2."],["p.para","As a family, read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/07/the-story-rug.p1"},"“The Story Rug”"],"(pages 4–5). Talk about your ancestors and play the",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/07/family-story-swap.p1"},"“Family Story Swap”"],"game (page 6)."]],["li",["span.label","3."],["p.para","Make a",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/07/bulletin-board.p1"},"time capsule"],"together (page 13). Collect pictures and mementos, and consider having each family member write their testimony on a piece of paper. Keep the time capsule in a safe place until you are ready to open it."]],["li",["span.label","4."],["p.para","Use the",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/07/families-are-part-of-heavenly-fathers-plan.p1"},"Bringing Primary Home"],"lesson and activity to learn more about this month’s Primary theme (pages 40–41)."]],["li",["span.label","5."],["p.para","Read",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/07/one-scoop-at-a-time.p1"},"“One Scoop at a Time”"],"(pages 18–19). Talk about some things your family can do to fill your lamps with oil. Get a jar like Lisa’s family did and add a scoop of dried beans, rice, or corn every time your family does something to keep the commandments."]]]]],[".resources",[".moreInfo",[".title","Hidden CTR Ring"],["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p9"},"Did you find the ring? Look on page 31!"]],[".moreInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p10"},"The",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"can be found on the Internet at",["a",{"href":"http://lds.org/friend"},"lds.org/friend"],". To subscribe online, go to",["a",{"href":"http://store.lds.org"},"store.lds.org"],"."]],[".moreInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p11"},"To send us a letter, drawing, or poem, please fill out this form and include it with your submission. Please also include a school photo or high-quality snapshot. Submissions will not be returned and may be edited for length and clarity. Children whose work is submitted should be at least three years old."],["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p12"},["span.emphasis","Please send your submission to:"]],[".address",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Magazine"],[".address","50 E. North Temple St., Rm. 2432"],[".address","Salt Lake City, UT 84150-0024"],[".address",["span.emphasis","Or email:"],["a",{"href":"mailto:friend@ldschurch.org"},"friend@ldschurch.org"]],["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p17"},["span.emphasis","The following information and permission must be included:"]],["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p18"},"Full name____________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p19"},"Age__________________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p20"},"State/Province, Country______________________"],["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/friend/2013/07/guide-to-the-friend.p21"},["span.emphasis","I agree to the terms of the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Submission Agreement (",["a",{"href":"http://lds.org/friend/parenta